rows.label: tev078202_MSG0001
rows.name:
Listen to this, [ST:playername ]! *fsssh*
I have successfully disgorged a new Zaruboggan![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078202_MSG0002
rows.name:
This never could have happened if you hadn't rescued
me in Noctilum. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078202_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell Arsenican that you're happy for him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078202_SEL0021
rows.name:
Ask Arsenican what exactly it
means to "disgorge" a child.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078202_MSG0005
rows.name:
Thank you kindly! I knew you were a good person,
through and through. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078202_MSG0006
rows.name:
If you wouldn't mind, I'd love for you to speak with
Orleron. I think it would be a valuable experience for
him to meet a [ST:gender p1=man  p2=woman  ]of your caliber. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078202_MSG0009
rows.name:
We are all the children of Golbogga. *fsssh*
What I did was merely disgorge a new life.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078202_MSG0010
rows.name:
If you are interested in the life I disgorged,
his name is Orleron. *fsssh* It would please me to
have you speak with him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078202_MSG0011
rows.name:
That should make it clear what exactly he is. *fsssh*
And I also think it would be valuable for him to meet a
person such as yourself.[ST:wait ]
